La domanda di conversione va presentata:
The conversion application must be submitted to the relevant Questura:
• **60 days before** turning 18, by the guardian;
• or **within 60 days after** turning 18, by the person directly concerned.

Per la conversione in permesso per lavor:
For conversion to an employed or self-employed work permit, an additional check on the contract requirements is required:
• **Validity of the signed contract**;
• **Compliance with the applicable collective bargaining agreement**;
• **Actual existence of the self-employed activity**, if applicable.

The check is carried out by labour consultants or by the employer associations.
